quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  42,1,"Haa, Miim : firo sugu …óee kalfe yawtiino ka fu…ó…óorde cortewol Al-baqarah."
  42,2,"Ain, Siin, Qaaf: firo sugu …óee kalfe yawtiino ka fu…ó…óorde cortewol Al-baqarah."
  42,3,"Ko sugu oo wayahu woni ko Allah wahayiniri e maa an Muhammdu, e …ìen Annabaa…ìe Makko adinoo…ìe ma, Allah Foolu…óo e yaggingol ay…ìe Mun, √ëee√±u…óo e toppitannde Mun e tagu Mun."
  42,4,"Ko Kanko Allah tun, woni ko jeyi kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi: tagugol e laamagol toppitoo. Ko Kanko kadi woni Toowu…óo e jaati Mun, fotde mum, poolgu e kattal Mun e toppitagol Mun, Mawnu…óo e jaati Mun."
  42,5,"Hino jeyaa e mawngu Allah ngun, tawde kammuuli …óin e no …ói foti e waade e toowude, hi…ói e…ì…ìa seekorgol dow leydi ndin, hara Malaa'ika'en no la…ì…ìinira Joomi ma…ì…ìe, yettugol Mo, yankinanoo Mo mawnina Mo, …ìe toroo Mo haforangol won…ìe ka leydi …ìen. Awa anndee pellet, ko Allah woni Haforanoowo kala tuubu…óo e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, Hinnotoo…óo …ìe."
  42,6,"∆Åen jogitii…ìe sanamuuji yi…ó…ìe rewetee…ói hara wanaa Allah, Allah na tommbii kuu…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen, O yo…ìitoyay …ìe …óe. An non Nulaa…óo, a wonaali fawaa…óo reenugol golle ma…ì…ìe, tawde a lamnditortaake kuu…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen. An on, ko a yottinoowo tun."
  42,7,"Ko wano Men wahayinirnoo e …ìeya Annabaa…ìe adinoo…ìe ma …ìen, Men wahayiniri e maa…óa an Nulaa…óo, janngeteende e haala aarabu, fii ko jertiniraa yim…ìe Makka …ìen e aarabuu…ìe won…ìe takko mayre …ìen, refti yim…ìe …ìen fow. Jertinaa kadi yim…ìe …ìen, fii √ëalande Darngal, √±alnde Allah moo…ìoyta adinoo…ìe e sakkitii…ìe fow nokku gooto, fii √±aaweede yo…ìee; √±alaande nde sikke alaa e mu'un. Yim…ìe …ìen wonoyay pecce …ói…ói: feccere goo, ka Aljanna; woni muumini'en, ndeya feccere, ka Yiite; woni heefer…ìe …ìen."
  42,8,"Si Allah haajuno, O wa…óayno fow e mofte goote ka lislaamu, O naada …ìe fow kadi Aljana. Kono √±en∆¥al Makko ngal e…ì…ìii nde O naadata mo O muuyi ka lislaamu, ontigi naatoya Aljanna. Too√±u…ìe non ko'e-mun geddi e keeferaaku, …ìe alaa gi…óo heftoowo fii ma…ì…ìe, wanaa walloowo …ìe e lepte Allah …óen."
  42,9,"Si ko woni, …ìee sirkoo…ìe jogiti yi…ó…ìe goo, ko wanaa Allah. Hara non ko Allah woni Gi…óo On tigiri, wanaa go…ó…óo goo nafatah maa lorra. Ko Kanko woni wuurnitoowo maay…ìe …ìen, fii hasbugol …ìe yo…ìa …ìe, huunde ronkintaa Mo."
  42,10,"Onon …ìee yim…ìe, kala ko luutondir…óon e fii mun ka doose diina maa ka cal…ói mun, haray √±aawoore mun nden, ko ka Allah woni: on ruttoto ka Deftere Makko maa ka Sunna Nulaa…óo Makko on (yo o his). Ko On sifor…óo …óin sifaaji, woni Joomi am; ko e Makko mi fawi fii am on fow, ko ka Makko kadi mi ruttorta tuubugol."